{"tid":977254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有膠先定有環保撚先","createTime":"2019-01-11T05:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T05:33:12.000Z","uid":52417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c669a994038af93bd64a88d2be0e738a98a108cf","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"我忍撚夠你班環保撚<br />\n首先就膠袋，我忍<br />\n之後杯蓋，搞到我成身可樂呀！你老母<br />\n之後飲管，搞到我拎飲管拎到成個乞衣咁<br />\n而家玩麥樂雞醬？分子料理呀？<br />\n我想正正常常食個麥當勞啫，點解搞鳩我！<br />\n遲下可能佢話魚卜可以代替condom<br />\n游水好過搭船，紙杯代替膠樽<br />\n到時我地真係乜膠都冇啦<br />\n所以第一步我地唔可以比佢地壯大<br />\n為生活！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw. 有時我真係懷疑你地係咪有心追擊M記<br />\n你地收咗幾多錢幫佢做宣傳？<br />\n根本就係一班用環保幫人賣廣告嘅偽善撚"},{"pid":"0255d831540a535ed38a02952482c87c5d75ff99","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37b3e4f5c7046e97ea68051397a04730d9f9d922","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"120df5d475babddb9d80c783d8e75a35fa325e3d","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd7cee9bf43eca7f98e27cea81da360f3b7e3e1","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51c2a03bb8109da6d5e8e2fd9a0e7780f50ab46","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13dc49bcac9ec084829d09a7536da27e351b5b3","tid":977254,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:33:12.000Z","msg